{"questionId":"87f513aa-a49e-436a-9a4c-c87bd3101b4c_17","correctAnswer":"28500","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"1 leuga = 7,500 pedes. Multiply to convert 3.8 leugas: 3.8 &times; 7,500."},{"title":"Solve","content":"3.8 &times; 7,500 = 3 &times; 7,500 + 0.8 &times; 7,500 = 22,500 + 6,000 = 28,500."},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>28500</strong> is correct."}]}